fields.name: Anthurium (Pink) - Plant
fields.description: Anthurium is a genus of about 1,000 species of flowering plants, native to the Americas. These plants are known for their bright flowers and can be used as a decorative indoor plant.

fields.name: Areca Palm (Small) - Plant
fields.description: Areca Palm is a popular houseplant and also known as Butterfly Palm. It is one of the most widely used palms for bright interiors. What makes it special: NASA recommended an air purifier plant. Popular indoor house plant. Best plant for AC rooms, office desk.

fields.name: Top 5 air purifier and oxygen enriching plant pack
fields.description: This plant pack includes the top 5 plants recommended by NASA for air purification and oxygen enrichment. Perfect for any home or office.

fields.name: Sansevieria trifasciata Hahnii, Snake Plant - Plant
fields.description: Sansevieria trifasciata Hahnii is a popular houseplant with dark green leaves marked with a pattern of wavy cross stripes in a lighter color. What makes it special: NASA recommended an air purifier plant. Best plant for AC rooms, office desk. Zero maintenance plant. Best indoor plant for low light condition.

fields.name: Aptenia, Heartleaf Ice - Succulent Plant
fields.description: Aptenia is a genus of succulent plants with heart-shaped leaves and bright flowers. These plants are perfect for indoor decoration and require minimal care.

fields.name: Rose (Red) - Plant
fields.description: Red Roses are a symbol of love and beauty. This plant can be grown indoors and is known for its vibrant red flowers.

fields.name: Hydrangea macrophylla (Any Color) - Plant
fields.description: Hydrangea macrophylla is known for its large and colorful flower heads. These plants are perfect for indoor decoration and can come in various colors.

fields.name: Set of 2 Bonsai Looking Grafted Adeniums
fields.description: This set includes two Bonsai looking Adenium plants. These plants are known for their unique appearance and are perfect for indoor decoration.
